{
  "texts": [
    "Case analysis of diseases with known associated circRNAsThe known associations are first applied to train CircDA.",
    "Next, disease-associated circRNAs are predicted using the trained model.",
    "After that, all candidate circRNAs are ranked according to the obtained prediction scores of all circRNAs.",
    "Finally, the predicted associations were validated by searching newly published literature.HCC is the most common malignancy worldwide.",
    "Accumulating evidence shows that circRNAs promote the growth of HCC cells."
  ]
}